    <h1>RAIoT Lab</h1>
    <h2>Robotics and IoT Innovation Hub at Amity University Jaipur, Rajasthan</h2>

    <div class="lab-info">
        <p>The <strong>RAIoT Lab</strong> at <strong>Amity University Jaipur</strong> is a cutting-edge research and innovation space dedicated to exploring advancements in Robotics and the Internet of Things (IoT). This lab empowers students from multiple branches to design and develop real-world solutions using the latest technologies.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Eligible Students:</strong> The RAIoT Lab is open to students from the following branches:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>B.Tech Computer Science and Engineering (CSE)</li>
            <li>B.Tech Information Technology (IT)</li>
            <li>B.Tech Mechanical Engineering</li>
            <li>B.Tech Electrical Engineering</li>
            <li>B.Tech Electronics and Communication Engineering</li>
            <li>Other related branches</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="project-examples"><strong>Innovative Projects:</strong> Students can develop a variety of innovative projects that contribute to different fields. Some examples include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Smart Google Glasses</li>
            <li>Smart Irrigation Systems</li>
            <li>Autonomous Drones</li>
            <li>Robotic Arms for Industrial Use</li>
            <li>IoT-based Home Automation Systems</li>
            <li>Healthcare Monitoring Devices</li>
        </ul>

